    "we can further test the predictions of the 1-to-1 network by examining putative information flow from the LCs to downstream circuits known to control chasing and singing.",
    "Here we develop knockout training, a novel solution to identify a one-to-one mapping between internal units in a DNN and real neurons in the brain of a fly.",
    "The model makes predictions about how neurons respond to sensory stimuli and drive behaviour.",
